 Five Housemates have won N400,000 each during the Hawaii challenge in the reality TV show. Laycon, Nengi, Prince, Wathoni and Praise were members of Team Hawaii Carrot, which won the challenge. The five Housemates won N2million tied to the challenge on Day 31 of the show. The Housemates on Wednesday August 19 were divided into three teams â€“ Team Hawaii Gold, Team Hawaii Carrot, and Team Hawaii Papaya -for the challenge.  They were asked to play some games and make a presentation. Team carrot won by 65 points, while had teams (Gold and Papaya) had 53 and 61 points respectively. After the games, the Housemates were each gifted with a box of Hawaii products.